<h1>Rabbit Adoption Submission</h1>
<h4>
  As a shelter, we rely on our web viewers to send in any rabbits they may have
  for adoption. Our staff will review each submission and make the rabbits
  available for adoption. We thank you for your contribution to our shelter.
</h4>

<form action="/rabbits" method="POST">
  Name: <input name="name" type="text" /><br />
  Img:<input name="img" type="text" /><br />
  Description: <input name="description" type="text" /><br />
  Age: <input name="age" type="text" /><br />
  Status: <input name="status" type="text" /><br />
  <input type="submit" value="Create Rabbit!" />
</form>

